    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/c3f55be537fc7806ca78c066117826e2.avif?t=1760625092\" width=607 height=142 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/2232e7aba5021a41087f92e4ec3053e1.poster.avif?t=1760625092\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/2232e7aba5021a41087f92e4ec3053e1.webm?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/2232e7aba5021a41087f92e4ec3053e1.mp4?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Enter the land of the undead</strong><br>Venture into randomly generated cemeteries in the land of the undead and explore the place where unknown forces have cursed everything and everyone present, so that in the end, you fulfill your great mission: find the sacred artifact and free Halloween from these evil spirits<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/4287b4ac13ee51e84955b04c0c6df25a.avif?t=1760625092\" width=607 height=142 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/7acd6e9a559f4cf4056512e1bae4fe0a.poster.avif?t=1760625092\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/7acd6e9a559f4cf4056512e1bae4fe0a.webm?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/7acd6e9a559f4cf4056512e1bae4fe0a.mp4?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Harness the evil power</strong><br>Enhance your equipment and character using items corrupted by unknown forces. Throughout the cemetery, you can find various cursed items that can have their malevolence channeled to aid you on your journey.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/5d457355f46b8a97a87097ba20b236b5.avif?t=1760625092\" width=607 height=142 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/35a836b2d249d6a09ef1b8232fc8935d.poster.avif?t=1760625092\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/35a836b2d249d6a09ef1b8232fc8935d.webm?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/35a836b2d249d6a09ef1b8232fc8935d.mp4?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Destroy all the corrupted</strong><br>The unknown forces have already infiltrated most of the beings in the cemetery. Now it's up to you to destroy everything that has been cursed to save the land of the undead and return them to a world free from evil.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/003bb527896eada14c35d2ea55f406a0.avif?t=1760625092\" width=607 height=142 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/e0f02149d89a39ff3427eb384011a16d.poster.avif?t=1760625092\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/e0f02149d89a39ff3427eb384011a16d.webm?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/e0f02149d89a39ff3427eb384011a16d.mp4?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Feel the Halloween spirit</strong><br>During your journey, you will encounter a mysterious purple-black cat who has a vast collection of corrupted items that can help you. The good news is that she loves treats and would trade anything for a handful of candy!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/86edb50a94501fe0aaf6e6ee7c796b07.avif?t=1760625092\" width=607 height=142 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/c9232fa81fcc483174025a4d16cf43e8.poster.avif?t=1760625092\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/c9232fa81fcc483174025a4d16cf43e8.webm?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041980/extras/c9232fa81fcc483174025a4d16cf43e8.mp4?t=1760625092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Scare the evil spirits</strong><br>With the help of mischievous masks, you can scare some spirits still wandering the cemetery in search of vulnerable beings. Just be careful they don't come back to pull your feet...",
